These are Puzzles for 6x3 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-7-1::.
House: futuristic, cape-cod, colonial
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: begonia, tulip, bellflower
The people have 3 different jobs:  nurse, analyst, musician
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, alhambra, dannemann
The people use 3 different means of transport: taxi, van, jet-ski
3 different games are played: backgammon, billiard, go
 1. the game-smoker is not the analyst##6
 2. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person playing backgammon##1
 3. the person who growsbellflower is somewhere to the left of the dannemann-smoker##5
 4. the person driving the jet-ski is somewhere between the futuristic house and the person playing go##7
 5. the person playing go is on the right of the dannemann-smoker##1
 6. the cape-cod house is the person playing backgammon##1
 7. the musician is not the person driving the van##6
 8. the person driving the taxi is on the left of the person who growstulip##1
 9. the alhambra-smoker is on the right of the musician##1
10. the person playing go is not the musician##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2     |     3     |
| House      | futuristic       | cape-cod  | colonial     |
| Flower          | bellflower       | tulip  | begonia    |
| Job         | nurse  | musician   | analyst |
| Cigar   | game | dannemann   | alhambra     |
| Transport   | taxi  | jet-ski | van   |
| Game           | billiard  | backgammon      | go  |

