There are 3 different favourite colors: apricot, lilac, aquamarine
3 different brands of cigars are smoked: ritmeester, swisher, bolivar
The people use 3 different means of transport: train, motorbike, roller
 1. the person driving the roller is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
 2. the person traveling to liverpool is somewhere to the left of the person driving the motorbike##5
 3. the person playing snooker is in the middle##1
 4. the person who likes aquamarine is somewhere between the person traveling to paris and the person drinking fanta##7
 5. the person playing snooker is not the person driving the train##6
 6. the person drinking sprite is between the ritmeester-smoker and the person who likes lilac##2
 7. the person driving the roller is on the left or right of the person who likes apricot##3
 8. the person playing snooker is somewhere between the person drinking fanta and the person playing backgammon##7
 9. the swisher-smoker is on the far left##1
10. the person traveling to paris is not the ritmeester-smoker##6

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |       2        |      3       |
