8. the person who's sport is rugby is somewhere between the fan swisherrot and the person traveling to hamburg##7
9. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the right of the fan swisherrot##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |      3      |
| City      | london       | rome      | hamburg    |
| Music-Genre          | swisherrot     | salsa        | reggae        |
| Pet           | goat  | fish | turtle   |
| Sport   | handball | rugby           | swimming |
| Color   | lilac  | yellow    | purple   |
| Cigar     | pall-mall        | baccarat          | swisher         |

