.:: Puzzle 6x3-Level-7-20::.
There 3 different types of food: plum, cucumber, corn
The people prefer 3 different music-genres: hip-hop, classical, punk
The people's birthday is in 3 different months: february, november, july
The people have 3 different hobbies: reading, dancing, cooking
The people grow 3 different varities of flowers: aconite, daisy, lily
There are 3 different favourite colors: white, black, purple
 1. the person eating plum is not the person who growsaconite##6
 2. the fan hip-hop is on the right of the person who likes white##1
 3. the person who's hobby is reading is somewhere between the person who's hobby is dancing and the person who's hobby is cooking##7
 4. the person eating corn is the fan punk##1
 5. the person who growsaconite is the fan punk##1
 6. the person who's hobby is reading is in an even position##4
 7. the person who growsdaisy is on the right of the person eating plum##1
 8. the person who's birthday is in february is the person who likes purple##1
 9. the person who growslily is somewhere to the right of the person who's birthday is in july##5
10. the person who's hobby is reading is the fan classical##1
11. the person who's hobby is dancing is somewhere to the right of the person who's hobby is cooking##5

.:: Answer ::.
